Package laazotea.indi

Provides some common classes for the INDI for Java Client, INDI for Java Driver and INDI for Java Server libraries.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INDIProtocolParser
    A interface representing a generic INDI Protocol Parser
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Base64  
    Base64.InputStream
    A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    Base64.OutputStream
    A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    ClassInstantiator
    A class to instantiate other classes based on their name and constructor parameters.
    Constants
    A class representing a some Constants and convenience functions to deal with them used in several parts of the INDI for Java libraries.
    INDIBLOBValue
    A class representing a INDI BLOB Value (some bytes and a format).
    INDIDateFormat
    A simple class to format and parse INDI timestamps.
    INDIProtocolReader
    A class that reads from a input stream and sends the read messages to a parser.
    INDISexagesimalFormatter
    A class to format and parse numbers in sexagesimal format.
    XMLToString
    A class to transforms XML Elements into Strings.
  • Enum Summary

    Constants.PropertyPermissions
    Possible perimssions for a INDI Property
    Constants.PropertyStates
    Possible States for a INDI Property
    Constants.SwitchRules
    Possible selection rules for a Switch Property.
    Constants.SwitchStatus
    Possible Switch Status Values.

Package laazotea.indi Description

Provides some common classes for the INDI for Java Client, INDI for Java Driver and INDI for Java Server libraries.
